# Himalaya HD (NetTV)
# The wmsAuthSign token expires ~24h after it is issued.
# Re-capture a fresh playlist.m3u8 URL daily and replace the line below.
# If it loads then fails in StreamVault (relative-URL re-encoding),
# swap the URL for the direct tokenized chunklist:
#   https://ott-nettv-02.nettv.com.np/ffplay/wc-Himalaya2/chunks.m3u8?wmsAuthSign=<TOKEN>
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-name="Himalaya HD" group-title="Nepal",Himalaya HD
#EXTVLCOPT:http-user-agent=Mozilla/5.0
https://ott-nettv-02.nettv.com.np/ffplay/wc-Himalaya2/playlist.m3u8?wmsAuthSign=c2VydmVyX3RpbWU9Ni8yMC8yMDI2IDI6MTI6MjAgUE0maGFzaF92YWx1ZT1PUHFSZVgzNVpUcDNudktGNDUyVmV3PT0mdmFsaWRtaW51dGVzPTE0NDAmaWQ9MjAw

